1
00:01:06,024 --> 00:01:08,026
<i>Some people are just bitter</i>

2
00:01:08,109 --> 00:01:10,695
because they can't conceive a baby.

3
00:01:10,779 --> 00:01:11,529
PREVIOUSLY

4
00:01:11,613 --> 00:01:13,239
George is infertile?

5
00:01:13,323 --> 00:01:17,327
One million jackpot prize
for the lucky guesser?

6
00:01:17,410 --> 00:01:20,330
You're really pulling out all the stops
for this party.

7
00:01:20,413 --> 00:01:21,998
- It's a boy!
- Yes!

8
00:01:22,082 --> 00:01:24,709
- It's a boy!
- It's a boy!

9
00:01:24,793 --> 00:01:26,753
- It's a boy!
- Congratulations!

10
00:01:26,836 --> 00:01:29,088
- We should choose the lucky guesser.
- All right, all right.

11
00:01:30,924 --> 00:01:32,217
It's George!

12
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:33,510
Yes!

13
00:01:33,593 --> 00:01:35,929
Get your prize. One million pesos.

14
00:01:36,012 --> 00:01:37,013
It's okay, Pa.

15
00:01:37,096 --> 00:01:38,807
You can give that to someone else.

16
00:01:38,890 --> 00:01:41,976
