It seemed like she was ready to kill.

26
00:02:08,670 --> 00:02:11,965
Oh, please! Don't remind me of it.
I just want to forget about it.

27
00:02:12,048 --> 00:02:13,591
<i>You had something to do with</i>
<i>what happened earlier.</i>

28
00:02:13,675 --> 00:02:16,010
Mother, I need to expose George's secrets.

29
00:02:16,094 --> 00:02:17,178
It's like the domino effect.

30
00:02:17,262 --> 00:02:18,513
One will fall after another

31
00:02:18,596 --> 00:02:22,016
until the truth comes out that she was
the mastermind behind Basil's death.

32
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:24,435
<i>- Who told you to touch my things?</i>
<i>- I did.</i>

33
00:02:24,519 --> 00:02:27,355
I asked them to transfer your things
and your family

34
00:02:27,438 --> 00:02:28,523
