36
00:02:33,778 --> 00:02:35,488
I am not kicking you out.

37
00:02:36,114 --> 00:02:38,950
I'm just giving space
between you and Beverly.

38
00:02:39,492 --> 00:02:40,910
Don't worry.

39
00:02:40,994 --> 00:02:44,998
You will still get your monthly allowance,
and for your family.

40
00:02:45,456 --> 00:02:46,666
But I was here first.

41
00:02:46,749 --> 00:02:48,376
