you're going to side with Ward?

76
00:04:33,147 --> 00:04:36,901
The reason we created Crimebusters
wasn't only to solve mysteries.

77
00:04:37,735 --> 00:04:41,656
Our friendship and loyalty
are important too.

78
00:04:41,739 --> 00:04:42,532
Oh my God.

79
00:04:42,615 --> 00:04:46,160
So now is not the time to drop Ward.

80
00:04:46,244 --> 00:04:48,371
Open your eyes, Sofia!

81
00:04:48,454 --> 00:04:50,331
Oh my gosh.

82
00:04:50,415 --> 00:04:51,457
Sofia?

83
00:04:52,208 --> 00:04:53,459
Please, Sofia.

84
00:04:53,543 --> 00:04:55,461
Don't side with that family!

85
00:04:56,296 --> 00:04:58,089
